      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d2402e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2424e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> Solicitations may use either a
performance work statement or a statement of objectives (see <xref href="37.602.dita#FAR_37_602"
                        base="i1077411"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">37.602</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2424e18">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Performance-based
contracts for services shall include-</p>
               <ol id="d2402e35" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2424e24">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> A performance
work statement (PWS);</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2424e29">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Measurable
performance standards (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">i.e.,</i> in terms of quality, timeliness,
quantity, etc.) and the method of assessing contractor performance
against performance standards; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2424e37">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph> Performance
incentives where appropriate. When used, the performance incentives
